    "Id": "vehicledef_GLADIUS_MKII",
    "Name": "Gladius Medium Hover Tank Mk II",
    "UIName": "Gladius Medium Hover Tank Mk II",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Gladius Medium Hover Tank Mk. II</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>8/12 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>145 ICE</color></b>\n\nCommissioned in 3042 by Imperator Marius O'Reilly, the Gladius Medium Hover Tank is a fast and simple combat vehicle. The tank is heavily armored for its size and uses a simple internal combustion engine, making it easy to produce and maintain. The Mark II is an upgrade to the hovertank's firepower. A Class 5 Light Autocannon and four Rocket Launcher 15s replace the original's single weapon. The tank is protected from infantry by an array of four Light Machine Guns. The tank has two tons of light autocannon ammunition, while the machine guns have half a ton.",
